<br>
We would be glad to hear from you, but first let me tell you what we are all about, and if your still interested after that, we can move on.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->        <br>
<br>
Colossus is a close knit group of people located on the Lanys server inside a game called Everquest.  We enjoy each others company and above all else are here to raid and further our characters careers.  Our currently scheduled raid nights are Sunday evening and Tuesday night.  For further information regarding raids and loot is dealt with, please see the Guild Rules posted in the Guild Rules section.  If we sound like a group of people you would be interested in, please continue reading.  <br>
<br>
The recruiting of Colossus members is one in which we feel is the best way to bring new members to our family. The only requirements in which to be accepted into Colossus are your main character must be at least 46+ and you have to have PoP enabled.<br>
<br>
The process of being recruited is as follows:<br>
<br>
1.  Contact any member about your interest in game.<br>
2.  Post here about your interest.<br>
3.  Get to know some of us and try to group with us.<br>
4.  Attend several guild raids so that your performance and personality can be seen by others in the guild.<br>
5.  And last but not least, dont be dumb.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
